ers and sisters are welcome to participate too admit weekend a celebration of writing readings by current and prospective stanford students friday april 27 2012 4 00 5 10 pm the stanford writing center holds the admit weekend open mic every spring to welcome stanford admits admits and all members of the stanford community are invited to read on subjects of their own choosing no advance sign up is required how i write in the how i write series brought to you by hilton obenzinger and continuing studies prominent stanford writers and researchers discuss their writing process hwc programs writing in the major introductory seminars honors writing and boot camp digital media consulting pwr stanford university 590 escondido mall stanford ca 94305 3069 650 723 2631 contact us terms of use copyright complaints site by wired moon
